name: unit-tests
description: Your task is to implement 'custom' version of the lodash library following next requirements: 1. Usage of `Array.prototype.*` or `Object.prototype.*` methods is **strictly forbidden**. (!!! Do not mix up *methods* and *properties* ) 2. You can create your own additional service functions (if needed). 3. You should use ES6+ features (any feature which supported by latest stable Chrome). 4. Lodash chain is out of scope
